title: UP-Guess Who's Coming to Christmas [2013]
description:
UP-Guess Who's Coming to Christmas (2013) 

Air Date: 8 Dec 2013

Summary: A jaded rock star, in order to repair his tarnished image, publicly agrees to fulfill a kid's Dear Santa Christmas wish. To his dismay, he ends up agreeing to spend the holidays in small town America and performing in the local holiday Christmas concert.

Drew Lachey ... Dax 
 
MacKenzie Porter ... Kelly Harding 
 
Evan Bird ... Tim Harding 
 
Olivia Cheng ... Chelsea 
 
Ellie Harvie ... Lynne Harding 
 
Peter LaCroix ... Reverend Harding 
 
Matt Ward ... Jason
